snippet.title: Divine Duel - Official Reveal Trailer
snippet.description:
Meet Vaya and Arvald in this reveal trailer for Divine Duel, an upcoming VR fighting game coming to lQuest 2 and Steam later in 2022. 

In Divine Duel, enter the magical world of Evergarden, take on the role of a powerful deity, and face off in spectacular duels against your peers.

#GameTrailers #Gaming #VR
